''' Â-pak-tên ''' ({{lang-en|Aberdeen}}), [[Yîn-koet]] [[Sû-kak-làn]] thi-khî ke chú-yeu sàng-sṳ chṳ̂-yit, he Sû-kak-làn 6 ke chṳ́ thin sṳ chûng, ngìn-khiéu phài-hàng thi-sâm ke sàng-sṳ (2013-ngièn sṳ̀ thúng-kie vì 227,130 ngìn <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.Gro-scotland.Gov.Uk/files2/stats/population-estimates/mid-2013/mid-2013-pop-est.Pdf|title=Table 2: Estimated population by sex, single year of age and administrative area, mid-2013|publisher=www.Gro-scotland.Gov.Uk/statistics/theme/population/estimates/mid-year/mid-2013/index.Html|accessdate=26 June 2014}}</ref>). Mien-chit 186km². Kâi sṳ vi-yî Sû-kak-làn tûng-pet-phu, pet-mien ke tun hò (River Don) lâu nàm-mien thit yî hò (River Dee) ke hò-khiéu chṳ̂-kiên, he [[Pet-hói (Thai-sî-yòng)| Pet-hói]] hói-pin ke chú-yeu [[hói-kóng]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.Gro-scotland.Gov.Uk/files2/stats/population-estimates/mid-2011/j22829707.Htm |title=Mid-2011 Population Estimates Scotland |publisher=Gro-scotland.Gov.Uk |date= |accessdate=8 November 2012}}</ref>
Chhai 18 Sṳ-ki chûng-ya̍p to 20 Sṳ-ki chûng-ya̍p ke 200-ngièn kiên, Â-pak-tên kien-chuk thúng-yit chhái-yung fôi-set Fâ-kong-ngâm, yîn yì yû “ Fâ-kong-ngâm sàng ” (Granite City) chṳ̂ chhṳ̂n, yu yîn-vì Fâ-kong-ngâm chûng yùn mû ke ngiùn set kông chhe̍t yì pûn chhṳ̂n-vì “ ngiùn sàng ” (Silver City). <ref name="agtb">{{cite web|url=http://www.Agtb.Org/aberdeen-scotland.Htm|publisher=Aberdeen and Grampian Tourist Board|title=The Granite City|accessdate=8 February 2007| archiveurl= http://web.Archive.Org/web/20070205064703/http://www.Agtb.Org/aberdeen-scotland.Htm| archivedate= 5 February 2007 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref> 1970-ngièn thoi fat-hien liáu [[Pet-hói yù thièn]] chṳ̂-heu yu fe̍t-tet liáu “ Êu-chû sa̍k yù chṳ̂ tû ” (Oil Capital of Europe) fò “ Êu-chû nèn-ngièn chṳ̂ tû ” (Energy Capital of Europe) tén chhṳ̂n-fû. <ref name="uni-abdn">{{cite web|url=http://www.Abdn.Ac.Uk/central/abdn/|title=About Aberdeen|publisher=University of Aberdeen |accessdate=8 February 2007| archiveurl= http://web.Archive.Org/web/20070205025539/http://www.Abdn.Ac.Uk/central/abdn/| archivedate= 5 February 2007 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>

